About

$

$

$
At Mallory Hill Country Club, our mission is to create an inviting and vibrant community where exceptional service, culinary excellence, and a warm atmosphere come together. We are committed to providing our guests with unforgettable dining experiences, all while experiencing our beautifully maintained golf course. Through dedication, innovation, and a passion for hospitality, we strive to be the premier destination for relaxation, enjoyment, and celebration in The Villages.
​
​
​
/$
/$
/$
/$
$
$
$
$
Dedicated Team
/$
$
Mallory's dedicated team consistently goes above and beyond to provide exceptional service, ensuring every guest experience is memorable and enjoyable.
/$
$
/$
$
/$
$
Delectable Dishes
/$
$
Mallory Hill specializes in classic American cuisine with a modern twist. Guests can enjoy a variety of dishes, from fresh seafood and tender steaks to hearty pastas and innovative chef specials.
/$
$
/$
$
/$
$
Golf Course Views
/$
$
At Mallory Hill Country Club Restaurant, guests are treated to breathtaking views of our meticulously maintained golf course. The expansive greenery and picturesque landscapes create a serene backdrop for a dining experience that's both relaxing and visually captivating.
